### Check server root
GET http://localhost:3000
Accept: application/json

###

### Setup database table (dev only)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/setup
Accept: application/json

###

### Add a new user
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ahmed",
  "balance": 500
}

